{"tid":2304460,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"賣鞋網Zappos創辦人謝家華逝世 終年46歲","createTime":"2020-11-28T20:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T04:47:31.000Z","uid":17387,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7e634fb168fb7a4affd35b853cea3253f2a44788","tid":2304460,"uid":17387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T20:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/n-FTHaSuvawaLqJvVMWTiObiioc=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VPMUJ2Q2RBDXPI4FH2JYQ55GSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fn-FTHaSuvawaLqJvVMWTiObiioc%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVPMUJ2Q2RBDXPI4FH2JYQ55GSQ.jpg&h=e05d2637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賣鞋網站Zappos行政總裁、美國億萬富豪謝家華（Tony Hsieh）日前因房屋失火而受傷，周五不治身亡，終年46歲。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）報道，謝家華創立的Downtown Partnership（DTP）公司發言人透露，謝家華日前在康湼狄格州拜訪家人時，因房屋失火而受傷，周五不治身亡，「謝家華的善良與慷慨感動了他周圍的每個人，永恆照亮這個世界」。<br />\n<br />\n謝家華在美國土生土長，畢業於哈佛大學計算機科學系，父母是移民美國的台灣人。1999年他創辦賣鞋網站Zappos，6年前售予網購平台亞馬遜後，繼續出任行政總裁。<br />\n<br />\n謝家華領導Zappos 20年後最近宣佈退休，Zappos的成功並未能滿足謝家華，他在Zappos總公司所在的拉斯維加斯發展一系列活化舊城區計劃，包括以貨櫃搭建的悠閒購物中心ContainerPark及作住宅用途的拖車公園。<br />\n<br />\n內華達州州長西索拉克（Steve Sisolak）在Twitter發文，「謝家華在協助改造拉斯維加斯市中心扮演關鍵角色......在這艱難時刻，我和太太向謝家華的至親好友致上慰問之意」。<br />\n<br />\n中央社／《蘋果》資料室<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201128/XK2ZWQWSI5C5NHBVULXNJGISEE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201128%2FXK2ZWQWSI5C5NHBVULXNJGISEE%2F&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=2386b6f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201128%2FXK2ZWQWSI5C5NHBVULXNJGISEE%2F&h=b7a961cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201128/XK2ZWQWSI5C5NHBVULXNJGISEE/</a>"},{"pid":"bf222a0b230f8c96c146c97df727e4425382905b","tid":2304460,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T00:34:07.000Z","msg":"Taiwan no 1"},{"pid":"e294e5ad43eb8814cd2b139090953a7445f55850","tid":2304460,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T02:31:52.000Z","msg":"幾廿億身家無命享"},{"pid":"2e4358bcab88b32007a2c553267450cffdc77ded","tid":2304460,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T02:42:10.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"06deb1ab5a62b698e03fb2909924f3b449d7bbba","tid":2304460,"uid":57462,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e294e5ad43eb8814cd2b139090953a7445f55850","tid":2304460,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T02:31:52.000Z","msg":"幾廿億身家無命享"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T02:46:51.000Z","msg":"你睇到人地睇唔到既野"},{"pid":"d83d93e613ea8482db543a926212bc7e210cfb10","tid":2304460,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:49:25.000Z","msg":"我睇過佢本書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8c00c81b89abaae393a6c546136673a25865a7","tid":2304460,"uid":209126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:58:10.000Z","msg":"佢係唔係支持拜登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8f6080669f7727651c71cb79ceae252f227fda","tid":2304460,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:59:31.000Z","msg":"46退休 然後都冇命享..."},{"pid":"9122e9cc9b9566fa5c3a342e6b6ced91e7f8a105","tid":2304460,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:59:34.000Z","msg":"Forbes estimated that he had a net worth of $840 million upon his retirement this summer.<br />\n<br />\n八億美金身家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9bc937bcef135dfd69629dd7cfea571825e1df2","tid":2304460,"uid":235152,"like":